Teen Number Train
.

Had a short #funmath session today exploring teen number (11 to 13). And before bed time we picked up a book about trains for our read. . . 
#stayandplayathomesg #stayhomeforsg #sgunited  #artthealphabet T is for TRAIN @startcreativestudio @brainy_beginnings_network #readalongplayalong @readalongplayalong #simpleplaywithnumbers @resources4learning @baby.bear.went.to.play #craftytransportation @craftymothering @flisatfun
